extendedInfo.description: In4mâ¢ is 4over IncÊ¼s job status app. It provides 4over Trade Members with real time job status. View jobs in ascending or descending order, display status based on stages in the production process, i.e: pre-press, print, shipping, etc. Search by job name or number; View details of any job, and cancel eligible jobs directly from the app. Track shipped jobs and share tracking information by email or copy and paste into a text message. Need more information about a job or have general questions, no problem, use In4mâ¢ to initiate a callback request.In4mâ¢ requires an active 4over trade account with a valid user-name and password. If you are a print reseller, you may apply for a 4over trade account at www.4over.com.4over, Inc. is the largest trade only printer in North America with facilities in CA, NJ, FL, TX, OH, IL, AZ, and ON, Canada.
